			<title>10.5: Enable X11 listening on port 6000</title>
			<link>http://feeds.macosxhints.com/click.phdo?i=094fe7fbb4cea31b87cad5196cd79b09</link>
			<pheedo:origLink>http://www.macosxhints.com/article.php?story=20081208062918906</pheedo:origLink>
